%indseqcondcell = cell(size(id,2),nconds,nconds); will be generated by NM2AllConditions
% this program calls  AnovaIndAnalysis to draw graphs for different
% configuration and stored them in specific subfolders, 

%NM2AllConditions; % load all data

Outdir = uigetdir('D:\Arian\Projects\SMART\Outputs\mintAtBHypoth\Individual\TripleSequenceAnova\','Select Output Upper Directory for the Graphs!'); 

